n我地更應該去尊重佢地決定既每一個step<br />\n而唔係任何情況下都係條命緊要 <br />\n條命緊要 咁當初衝入去做咩？ 你覺得佢地係諗住安然無事出番黎咩？<br />\n佢地一定係諗好哂先做 而唔係一時三刻魯莽既草率決定<br />\n好多事都係做左先知 當然你可以話救左先 可能佢地唔想死<br />\n但事實係 你我都唔係佢地條蟲 又憑咩去幫手決定人地既去留呢？"},{"pid":"7a6e7b57b35c255556d48609d92f734a1fd7c948","tid":1280491,"uid":12185,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"一句講曬，冇衝過嘅又得閒咪出去搵，最重要唔好用過高成本"},{"pid":"ba81bad682057a8574eb6d13e7be3380a15b7a75","tid":1280491,"uid":88785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a6e7b57b35c255556d48609d92f734a1fd7c948","tid":1280491,"uid":12185,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"一句講曬，冇衝過嘅又得閒咪出去搵，最重要唔好用過高成本"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:38:31.000Z","msg":"我同意<br />\n但各位要記得 要用自己個腦去分析<br />\n任何人講既野都只供參考 直至你眼見為實<br />\n包括我講既野 大家都只應該參考<br />\n而唔係用哂人力物力去搵一個用字打出黎既人/做任何一個網民叫你做既野"},{"pid":"42c590561ba0db346d582121ae9583b834a6a795","tid":1280491,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qmvZYVv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqmvZYVv.jpg&h=1411f016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u83492g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu83492g.jpg&h=d30363dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCX2cfH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCX2cfH.jpg&h=d2d279fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12wa5AT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12wa5AT.jpg&h=5395cbf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"055544bd2044acaefd33cabe85894be9c6b89c6b","tid":1280491,"uid":89882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:40:21.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n要贏 一定要清楚自己做緊咩"},{"pid":"152e17629c45e56a84af6188f4597baff8a0ca8c","tid":1280491,"uid":88785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime